snippet.textDisplay:
A great rock interpretation of #Bhoberpagol. The bassist could have slapped the bass to further compliment this awesome powerful rendition by Nigar Sumi.
Not sure about the rap that's been forced into the song. Transition from one genre to the other could have been addressed in a more creative way like it had been done in Kattey by Hard Kaur, Bhanvari Devi in Coke Studio.
